sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant PE as /pi-end
    participant PIR as /pir
    participant PI as ~/.claude/pi/[current-pi]/
    participant Co as ~/.claude/companies/[name]/
    participant FS as docs/

    H->>PE: /pi-end

    note over PE: AFK prep
    PE->>PI: Read plan.md (all features + release targets)
    PE->>FS: Read sprint records + DEVLOG for the PI period
    PE->>Co: Read tokens/ledger.md (PI token total)

    PE->>PI: Archive PI plan
    PE->>Co: Generate stakeholder delivery summary
    PE->>H: PI token total surfaced from ledger

    PE->>H: Present PI close summary — confirm
    H->>PE: Confirmed

    note over H,Co: Post Implementation Review
    H->>PIR: /pir PI-N

    PIR->>FS: Read all feature PRDs + /approve records for PI-N
    PIR->>FS: Read qa-plan results + known-issues

    note over PIR: HITL outcome assessment (per feature)
    loop Each delivered feature
        PIR->>H: Did [feature] achieve its stated goals?
        PIR->>H: Evidence? Metrics vs targets? Assumptions validated?
        H->>PIR: Assessment
    end

    PIR->>Co: Save pir/PI-N/pir-YYYY-MM-DD.md
    PIR->>H: PIR gaps feed /fy-review as primary data source

    note over H,Co: Optional
    H->>Co: /fy-review — annual review across all PI outcomes
